PrecisAppointment of THOMAS P. LAUGHLIN., K.C., of Stratford, in the Province of Prince Edward Island, one of His Majesty’s Counsel learned in the law, be appointed a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Prince Edward Island, and a Judge ex officio of the Supreme Court of Prince Edward Island.
